name: OG: Wild Wars- Alien Organisms
description:
OG is for Old Game. I made this game with GameMaker 6 when I was about 12 (I updated it at some point, but I was most likely 12 for this version).

Select the units you want to send out by clicking on them and defeat the enemy saucer!

TitleWild Wars- Alien OrganismsEstimated Release Date2007? (I have 9/24/2006 for a version, but I updated it. this seems to have some of the updates)My Age at the Time12(?)My Rating Now4.5/10My Rating Then (Probably)9/10EngineGameMaker 6.0
